des:
LUX Control  products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your LUX Control products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "LUX Control " app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "LUX Control " app;
(3). You need to have some LUX Control  devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "LUX Control " app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "LUX Control " skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "LUX Control " skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "LUX Control ", and you'll be navigated to "LUX Control " login page;
(9). Open "LUX Control" App, click More Service, choose "Alexa". Link with Verification Code, copy the Code, put code into the login page；
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
